snippet.title: Tartapolis
snippet.description:
Check it out and wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1072110/Tartapolis/

Welcome to the City! Built upon a great crater, full of shady individuals and secrets is home to the protagonist Richard Bor. Follow his footsteps as he uncovers a great secret about Tartapolis!
